snippet: The Dallas Cowboys unseated Spanish soccer club Real Madrid for top spot on a list of the world's 50 most valuable sports teams, according to a Forbes poll released on Wednesday that was dominated by NFL franchises....
lead_paragraph: The Dallas Cowboys unseated Spanish soccer club Real Madrid for top spot on a list of the world's 50 most valuable sports teams, according to a Forbes poll released on Wednesday that was dominated by NFL franchises.

headline.main: Dallas Cowboys Top Forbes' Most Valuable Teams List
headline.print_headline: Dallas Cowboys Top Forbes' Most Valuable Teams List
